Package com.github.dm.rf.android.filter

Package containing classes defining filtering of elements, keys and values.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdvancedFilter<E>
    This interface defines an advanced element filter.
    AdvancedFilter.FilterIterator<E>
    This interface defines an iterator resulting from the application of filters to the sparse array iterable.
    BooleanFilter
    This interface defines a filter of boolean elements.
    BooleanFilterBuilder
    This interface defines a FilterBuilder associated with BooleanSparseIterable objects.
    Filter<E>
    This interface defines a filter used to include or exclude elements, matching a specific condition, from the iteration.
    FilterBuilder<T extends SparseIterable<E>,E>
    This interface defines a builder of filters associated with a SparseIterable instance.
    IntFilter
    This interface defines a filter of int values.
    IntFilterBuilder
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling int elements.
    LongFilter
    This interface defines a filter of int values.
    LongFilterBuilder
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling long elements.
    LongSparseArrayFilterBuilder<V>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling LongSparseArrayEntry elements.
    SimpleArrayMapFilterBuilder<K,V>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SimpleArrayMapEntry elements.
    SparseArrayCompatFilterBuilder<V>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseArrayEntry elements.
    SparseArrayFilterBuilder<V>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseArrayEntry elements.
    SparseBooleanArrayFilterBuilder
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseBooleanArrayEntry elements.
    SparseIntArrayFilterBuilder
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseIntArrayEntry elements.
    SparseLongArrayFilterBuilder
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling SparseLongArrayEntry elements.
    SupportLongSparseArrayFilterBuilder<V>
    This interface extends the FilterBuilder one by providing specific methods handling LongSparseArrayEntry elements.
